00:00:57.420 --> 00:01:01.710
the piece is to process it to make
it sound really distanct as though

00:01:01.710 --> 00:01:05.990
it is coming over a shortwave radio.
And then he has Morse Code, and

00:01:05.990 --> 00:01:10.280
there is various Morse Code messages
going through the piece.

00:01:10.280 --> 00:01:14.570
Wireless Fantasy, from 1960,
done long-hand, by the way. It was

00:01:14.570 --> 00:01:18.850
really done with Morse Code in a
mainframe computer and giant

00:01:18.850 --> 00:01:23.120
